data.description: This charming 3 bed/1.5 bath is minutes away from Sheppard AFB! Buyers will enjoy the ample space & storage in all 3 bedrooms with large step-in closets. Open concept kitchen with plenty of cabinet space & a living room that features a wood burning fireplace. Brand new floors & windows throughout the entire home. Large backyard with a covered patio, privacy fencing ,mature trees & a storage shed with electricity. New security system installed & solar panels for low to no electric bills at all!
